headline.main: EDEN PRAISES WORK OF GEN. EISENHOWER; Says Staff of American Has no Parallel in History

lead_paragraph: LONDON, July 1 -- Foreign Secretary Anthony Eden highly praised the "invaluable work" of General Dwight D. Eisenhower in his address tonight before the English-Speaking Union, which celebrated its twenty-fifth anniversary.
